<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-icarus-500 mb-2">Static JSON API</h1>
  <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8">
    Project Daedalus exposes its data as plain JSON files served straight off the static site —
    no API key, no rate limit beyond what GitHub Pages does, no auth. Useful for mod managers,
    Discord bots, dashboards, or any tool that wants to consume the catalog.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-icarus-500 mt-8 mb-3">Endpoints (v1)</h2>
  <div class="grid gap-3">
    <a href="./v1/mods.json" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 no-underline hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <code class="font-mono text-icarus-500 text-sm md:text-base">/api/v1/mods.json</code>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">array of mod docs</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Every curated mod in the catalog. Includes name, author, version, compatibility, files, image_url, readme_url, description.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="./v1/tools.json" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 no-underline hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <code class="font-mono text-icarus-500 text-sm md:text-base">/api/v1/tools.json</code>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">array of tool docs</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Community modding tools (mod managers, validators, editors).</p>
    </a>
    <a href="./v1/nexus_mods.json" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 no-underline hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <code class="font-mono text-icarus-500 text-sm md:text-base">/api/v1/nexus_mods.json</code>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">array of Nexus mods</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Icarus mods hosted on Nexus Mods, with derived game-week from upload/update timestamps.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="./v1/info_content.json" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 no-underline hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/80">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <code class="font-mono text-icarus-500 text-sm md:text-base">/api/v1/info_content.json</code>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">array of info cards</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Cards rendered on the Info page (Discord links, guides, etc.).</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-icarus-500 mt-8 mb-3">Other syndication</h2>
  <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
    <li>📡 <a href="../feed.xml" class="text-icarus-500 hover:underline font-mono">/feed.xml</a> — Atom feed of recent mods (top 50)</li>
    <li>🗺️ <a href="../sitemap.xml" class="text-icarus-500 hover:underline font-mono">/sitemap.xml</a> — every page on the site</li>
    <li>🤖 <a href="../robots.txt" class="text-icarus-500 hover:underline font-mono">/robots.txt</a> — crawl-allow + sitemap pointer</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-icarus-500 mt-8 mb-3">Data freshness</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
    The bundled JSON is regenerated by the hourly <a href="https://github.com/DonovanMods/project_daedalus/actions/workflows/sync-mods.yml" class="text-icarus-500 hover:underline">sync-mods workflow</a>. Treat <code class="font-mono">/api/v1/mods.json</code> as a hourly snapshot, not a live feed.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-icarus-500 mt-8 mb-3">Stability and versioning</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
    The <code class="font-mono">/api/v1/</code> URLs are stable. Field additions are non-breaking; field removals or renames will only happen behind a new version (<code class="font-mono">/api/v2/</code>) and the v1 URLs will keep working.
  </p>
</section>
